  <brief_title>A Comparative Study of Brain Structure and Amyloid Load in MCI Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparative Study of Brain Structure and Amyloid Load Between Cognitively Impaired Older People With or Without Diabetes Mellitus</official_title>
